node.text:
We speak with @angeliquekidjo about performing a rendition of the iconic anthem - Imagine, for the #tokyo2020 Opening Ceremony.

She shares her joy in seeing @naomiosaka lighting the Olympic flame and looks forward to world uniting through peace in sport for the next 16 days of Olympic competition.

#strongertogether

node.text:
We catch up with 3,000m steeplechase runner @steeple_squigs ahead of #tokyo2020 Opening Ceremony tomorrow. 🇺🇸 

The 28-year-old will not be competing in Tokyo and speaks to @ash_tulloch about withdrawing from the U.S. Olympic trails last month due to her body needing a break. She says she is at peace with her decision despite missing being at her second Games. 

The Rio 2016 Olympian gives her predictions for her specialty event, shares some advice for athletes competing in the Games and can’t wait to watch the competition when it’s gets underway. 

#strongertogether @teamusa @usatf
